value.title: Leopard.FYI for Women & Non-Binary Software Engineers
value.description:
About Event

​We're hosting a low-key happy hour hang in San Francisco for Talent & People Leaders across the broader Leopard network 💜

​When: Jan 8, 2025 from 6-9 PM 📆

​Where: Yerba Buena Bar in SOMA 🪩

​Food: Open Bar & Appetizers from Raavi (Samosas, Kebabs & Naan) covered by Leopard 💜

​Who is invited? Vetted People & Talent Leaders (including teams of 1 at startups) who believe in inclusivity in tech. Our private people/talent Slack community has 350+ members & includes leaders from Huggi
